OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1778087158
OL,3,CNewest generation of fire cadets
OL,4,Cgraduate in Cumbria
OL,6,FThe newest generation of fire cadets
OL,7,Fhave graduated in Cumbria following a
OL,8,Fnine-week training programme.
OL,10,FCumbria Fire and Rescue Service has
OL,11,Fexpanded its fire cadets scheme with
OL,12,Fthe launch of new units across the
OL,13,Fcounty including in Whitehaven and
OL,14,FCarlisle. It is already building on
OL,15,Fthe successful unit in Workington.
OL,17,FThe fire cadets had their passing-out
OL,18,Fparade to mark the completion of their
OL,19,Ftraining.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
