PN,35602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1778087158
OL,3,CNewest generation of fire cadets
OL,4,Cgraduate in Cumbria
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Border, fire cadet
OL,7,FBeth said: "I've 100% grown my
OL,8,Fconfidence, when I first joined I
OL,9,Fwouldn't shout, I wouldn't do
OL,10,Fanything, and now if you ask anyone I
OL,11,Fcan't stop talking.
OL,13,F"I'm always there to help people, I'll
OL,14,Fnever not help people. I've seen a
OL,15,Fvariety of people from all backgrounds
OL,16,Fand all behaviours join cadets and
OL,17,Fbecome a better person and become more
OL,18,Fconfident in themselves, so I
OL,19,Fdefinitely recommend it to anyone."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
