PN,35603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1778087158
OL,3,CNewest generation of fire cadets
OL,4,Cgraduate in Cumbria
OL,6,FPaige also shares the same view and
OL,7,Fbelieves that her experience will give
OL,8,Fher valuable life skills moving
OL,9,Fforward.
OL,11,FShe said: "I was such a nervous
OL,12,Fperson. And joining a group full of
OL,13,Fboys that were all older than you,
OL,14,Fcould be intimidating and like, as a
OL,15,Flittle 12 year old, I was really,
OL,16,Freally scared.
OL,18,F"But you sound like when we're doing
OL,19,Fdrills, you soon learn everyone's a
OL,20,Fbig family. We've learned so much."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
