PN,35604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1778087158
OL,3,CNewest generation of fire cadets
OL,4,Cgraduate in Cumbria
OL,6,FAssistant Chief Fire Officer for
OL,7,FCumbria Fire and Rescue Service,
OL,8,FLauren Woodward is hoping that some of
OL,9,Fthe cadets take the inspiration and
OL,10,Fbecome fire fighters.
OL,12,FShe said: "hey really are doing a
OL,13,Ffirefighter's role. Hopefully some
OL,14,Fwill come on and work for Cumbria Fire
OL,15,Fand Rescue Service, but, you know,
OL,16,Fgoing and contributing to their
OL,17,Fcommunities, which is a massive part
OL,18,Fof Cumbria.
OL,20,F"It's about giving them that stepping
OL,21,Fstone to be able to do that.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
