PN,35605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1778087158
OL,3,CNewest generation of fire cadets
OL,4,Cgraduate in Cumbria
OL,6,F"So it's vital, I think, in terms of
OL,7,Fshaping their futures, and they all
OL,8,Fbecome ambassadors for us as a service
OL,9,Fas well to spread our safety messages."
OL,11,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,12,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,13,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,14,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,15,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,16,Fbelow...
